channel.title: RscF2P Pk Server\Skilling - 24-7. Quests, 150x for a week! Rscd Based - Online
channel.description:
[b]RscF2P Pk\Skill[/b] [IMG]http://i294.photobucket.com/albums/mm105/anc13nts/RscF2P.jpg[/img]
We Bring you a [b]RscF2P[/b] server which is easy for pking and Skilling but it will need just a little work. We have upped the Xp rate from 30x to [b]150x[/b] for maybe a week or two, this will help get players and boost the economy so get the xp rate while you can!
We have a Fully Working Quest System which where we will be implementing F2P quests in. Pretty much everything is fixed. We Removed all Member items, if you find any that shouldn't be in the game Please report it to an Administrator. [b]EXP Rate: [s]30x[/s]150x[/b] Getting a 99 stat won't take that long. Getting Rune Etc must be smithed. Won't take long there are a few smithers from beta testing already.
We are [b]24-7[/b], We can withstand MOST DDoS attacks with our 127k ConCurrent Session Firewall. We Are Also on a Dedicated Server, don't expect us to go down. Rscd V25 based. Join now. Reg Size Client Download - http://www.speedyshare.com/130150425.html
Big Size Client Download - http://www.speedyshare.com/538806252.html Link in sig.
